# Editor Development
./clusterfile-editor.sh build
./clusterfile-editor.sh run
./clusterfile-editor.sh release patch|minor|major

# Testing
python3 tests/run_tests.py

# Container
podman run --rm --network=host quay.io/dds/clusterfile-editor:latest
```

